It appears to be a microbe that was found on the bottom of Mono Lake in Yosemite National Park, California, where it lives in an environment that was considered too toxic for any life form, as the lake is rich in arsenic.
The creature somehow uses arsenic to sustain its life, and it's this ability that makes it more likely that similar life could exist on other planets that don't have Earth-like atmospheres.
